"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-27-Medal-events-to-follow-at-2024-Paris-Summer-Olympics-on-July-27-1vzRHQBc4es-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  The competitions will continue at the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics on Saturday night with more gold medals decided in the French capital.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 362, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 347, \"end\": 353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9917005950124952, \"rank\": 0.0067968574627559845, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN Sports Scene has the rundown for all of the finals taking place in the evening session on the first full day of competition at the Games.\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 363, \"end\": 367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.668094869111489e-17, \"text\": \"CGTN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's skateboarding\\u00a0street final will begin at 17:00 (GMT+2) at the Place de la Concord.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Concord_Records\", \"score\": 0.6209364472155466, \"rank\": 0.58528709954258, \"text\": \"Concord\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q18127\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Concord_Records\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Concord_Records\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In swimming, the mens and women's 400-meter freestyle finals will take place at the Olympic Aquatics Centre in the Paris La Defense Arena at 20:42 (GMT+2), followed by the men's and women's 4\\u00c3\\u0097100-meter freestyle relay finals at 21:34 (GMT+2).\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the women's fencing epee individual gold medal bout will get underway at the Grand Palais at 21:30 (GMT+2).\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 1219, \"entities\": []}]}"